        <Parent_String>Crustacea (subphylum) [300310469], Arthropoda (phylum) [300265687], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a class of around 23,000 species of ancient, relatively small, primarily marine crustaceans including barnacles, copepods, mystacocarids, tantulocarids, branchiurans, ostracods, and related groups, having five pairs of head appendages, a single median eye, and up to 11 trunk segments.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>包含約兩萬三千種小型甲殼綱動物，大多數為海生動物，包括藤壺、橈足類動物、須蝦類動物、微蝦類動物、鰓尾類動物、介形類動物及其他相關物種群。有五對頭部附肢，以及一隻位於中央的眼睛，體節高達11節。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Klasse van circa 23.000 soorten zeer oude, betrekkelijk kleine en overwegend in zee levende kreeftachtigen waartoe zeepokken, roeipootkreeften, mystacocarida, tantulocarida, branchiura, ostracoda en daarmee verwante groepen behoren. Ze hebben vijf paren kopaanhangsels, één oog in het midden en tot 11 achterlijfsegmenten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
